{
  "stem": "1491.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were talking about being back in Plaszow and watching your father going away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] of course, they had no work for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they had to do something with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put us in barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never forget the middle of the night, I was covered with bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I am scared of any animal, any insect, or anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I risked my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I took out the-- I went out from the barracks and I slept outside the barracks on the ground, because I couldn't take the bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was covered from top to bottom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put us in barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, they didn't have work for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't know what to do with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who were you in the barracks with this time?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Were you with your mother and sister?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was with my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had a younger sister, which I had to protect her too, I mean cover up, because wherever we work you had to push out so-- we worked in a brush factory for a while, so you had to push out so many, so many brushes.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was a child, so she couldn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I helped her with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was constant fear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in that brush factory where we were working, there was a special like cemetery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to bring Jews from-- who were hiding on Aryan papers in Krakow, and they caught them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they used to bring them and the children, and they were killing them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had to undress, put down their clothes on the ground, and jump to that grave.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
